Fwww.facebook.com%2Fk11ArtMall%2F&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=12edb530\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/k11ArtMall/</a><br />\n<br />\nGucci<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GucciHongKong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGucciHongKong%2F&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=2266e62c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/GucciHongKong/</a><br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Email template:</strong></span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSubject<br />\n<br />\nPlease ensure the safety of our staff on 5th August Strike<br />\n<br />\nContent <br />\n<br />\nDear Management of ____,  <br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of concerned Hong Kong citizens writing to inquire about the upcoming strike. According to sources as diverse as newspaper headlines (see attached link below) and various discussions on Facebook and web forums, a major strike is expected on 5th August (next Monday), with large scale assembly is also expected in our area. I am worried for both public safety and public transportation logistics for the day. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ORDINANCE, CHAPTER 509, Employers should contribute to safety and health in their workplaces by: <br />\n* providing and maintaining safe access to and egress from the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nWe appreciate your response by 8PM today (2 August 2019).<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=c1813635\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"f76802e659e306d67f06878e856bce16a45ec09a","tid":1396510,"uid":149487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af524b1969b85ad7122b3b19967966049d743eaa","tid":1396510,"uid":278391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c66e8e30d4acb22325a91538de6005f8b5af3970","tid":1396510,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係咁<br />\n前一晚食啲熱氣嘢, 喉嚨點都有少少紅腫<br />\n跟住就話尋晚發過燒, 有咳有鼻水<br />\nAchievement unlocked: URTI"},{"pid":"c1155166cbe601dc928e95e56623df01556a4c8d","tid":1396510,"uid":113335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:33:42.000Z","msg":"同個醫生講光復香港 時代革命 就知架啦"}]}